text: Natalia Viktorovna Razumovskaya () (born 18 August 1975) is a Russian freestyle skier. She won a gold medal at the FIS Freestyle World Ski Championships 1999 in Meiringen-Hasliberg. == References == == External links == * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Russian female freestyle skiers
